    <h1 class="subtitle">
        Hi, I'm zackdcat.
    </h1>

    <p class="AboutMe">
		Hi, I'm zack (zackdcat), a programmer from the UK.
		<br><br>
		This is my personal portfolio website which I self host.
		I enjoy building things for the web and creating
		Minecraft mods. Most of my work is
		with HTML, CSS and JavaScript.
		<br><br>
		I use vscode for most projects but for some I will use an intellij ide. I also use ubuntu linux as my main os.
		<br><br>
		I use github for my projects, modrinth for my minecraft projects and ko-fi for support and <a href="https://ko-fi.com/zackdcat/shop">paid projects</a>.
		<br><br>
		I also self host a minecraft server. <br>
		Ip/domain: <span class="copyable" onclick="copyToClipboard(this)">mc.zackdcat.site</span> <- Copy.
		<br><br>
		You can email me <a href="mailto:zwhseton@gmail.com">here</a> if you have any in enquiries.
		
	</p>

